Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.

des: This is for entertainment purposes. It provides dog names on request to help you pick a name for your dog. Say male, female, neutral or any for a gender-specific dog name. It does not require any permissions or customer data.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
